Ghost looming waiting to pounce Legend says that he was born when a cloud became too heavy and fell out of the sky. The spirits of the island took pity on the cloud, and gave it physical form. A young and playful spirit, you will find him zooming all around the island. Too young to have yet realized his own vulnerability, this spirit relies on other spirits to ensure its safety and the safety of the island.SETUP:Put 1 {presence} on your starting board in the corner furthest from all other playersPlay Style:Extremely mobile and difficult to kill. Exceptionally good at generating fear, but requires coordination with teammates for the full power of this spirit to be realized.
